    <summary>Clara and the Lost Button</summary>
    <div class="details-content">
        <p>Clara found a small blue button on the sidewalk. It looked forgotten, so she picked it up.</p>
        <p>At school, she saw a boy searching the ground. “Lose something?” she asked.</p>
        <p>“My grandpa’s button,” he said.</p>
        <p>Clara smiled and held it out. “This one?”</p>
        <p>He nodded, eyes wide.</p>
        <p>She handed it over. “It was waiting for you.”</p>
    </div>
</details>

