    <div class="details-content">
        <p>Clara found a fallen nest under her favorite tree. Two tiny eggs inside—safe, but far from home.</p>
        <p>She waited.</p>
        <p>A passing gardener noticed. “Need help?”</p>
        <p>Together, they returned the nest.</p>
        <p>Clara smiled. The tree stood quietly, watching.</p>
    </div>
